item.title: CVE-2020-14180|2024-09-17T01:26:00.604Z -- atlassian -- jira%20service%20desk%20server
item.description: Affected versions of Atlassian Jira Service Desk Server and Data Center allow remote attackers authenticated as a non-administrator user to view Project Request-Types and Descriptions, via an Information Disclosure vulnerability in the editform request-type-fields resource. The affected versions are before version 4.12.0.
